[SPEAKER_03]: The town where I live here in the state has a specific stabilization fund for fire department asset depreciation.

669
01:09:37,042 --> 01:09:42,526
[SPEAKER_03]: So we fund that every year so that when it comes time to replace a fire engine, we don't have to go for debt.

