728
01:15:25,494 --> 01:15:33,441
[SPEAKER_03]: That really has to do with not only the kind of scope of work of the departments, but really what capital assets they have custody of.

729
01:15:33,821 --> 01:15:38,705
[SPEAKER_03]: And so you can see DPW and engineering have many, many projects, more than 50% of the projects.

730
