748
01:17:27,623 --> 01:17:40,126
[SPEAKER_04]: And if we took the, and again, this isn't a criticism of, it's just a comment because I think it goes back to the, you know, here's what we're putting in, but what is our actual need, you know, engineering over six fiscal years, let's call it 18 million.

749
01:17:40,146 --> 01:17:40,867
[SPEAKER_04]: Let's call it like 3.

750
01:17:41,167 --> 01:17:42,027
[SPEAKER_04]: Something million a year.

751
01:17:42,567 --> 01:17:45,709
[SPEAKER_04]: Let's assume all those engineering projects or roads and sidewalk projects.

752
01:17:46,149 --> 01:17:49,230
[SPEAKER_04]: We're doing about 3 million year which is great and it's more than we were doing before.

753
01:17:49,790 --> 01:17:59,575
