756
01:18:28,220 --> 01:18:31,182
[SPEAKER_04]: 170 million if our need is a billion, not so good.

757
01:18:32,283 --> 01:18:37,007
[SPEAKER_04]: But yeah, it's really just more of a comment and I really appreciate this chart and thank you for answering my question.

758
01:18:38,031 --> 01:18:39,732
[SPEAKER_03]: Yeah, Councillor, I mean, it's a great point.

759
01:18:40,772 --> 01:18:46,414
