760
01:18:46,594 --> 01:18:47,895
[SPEAKER_03]: So that's really the trick.

761
01:18:49,615 --> 01:18:54,157
[SPEAKER_03]: You know, it would be great if we had $100 million to spend on the roads to make them perfect.

762
01:18:56,118 --> 01:19:07,462
