01:20:24,432 --> 01:20:28,233
[SPEAKER_03]: So if I told you that you had a million dollars to spend in free cash after you

781
01:20:28,993 --> 01:20:38,164
[SPEAKER_03]: listed all the projects that you wanted to actually spend and complete, I could then tell you, OK, you've got $50,000 left or you're over by $50,000.

782
01:20:38,424 --> 01:20:41,448
[SPEAKER_03]: You need to cut a project that is about that amount.

783
01:20:41,508 --> 01:20:45,052
[SPEAKER_03]: So that's what I mean when I say surplus or deficit compared to the target.

784
01:20:45,833 --> 01:20:48,796
