[SPEAKER_03]: The reason that you see such small numbers for 24 and 25 and 26

807
01:23:20,258 --> 01:23:36,913
[SPEAKER_03]: and actually 27 too, is because when you do such a major building projects, you're issuing bans, bond anticipation notes, which means you're only paying a very small amount until you issue the full amount of the debt once the construction has gone forward.

808
01:23:38,275 --> 01:23:40,056
[SPEAKER_02]: So you can see that.

809
