821
01:24:40,446 --> 01:24:42,807
[SPEAKER_03]: So this is just new projects on this table.

822
01:24:44,148 --> 01:24:50,012
[SPEAKER_03]: The existing debt service inclusive of the library issuance was in the existing debt already committed.

823
01:24:50,052 --> 01:24:51,913
[SPEAKER_03]: So that has been accounted for, absolutely.

824
01:24:51,933 --> 01:24:53,934
[SPEAKER_07]: Thank you.

825
01:24:54,315 --> 01:24:57,176
[SPEAKER_03]: Thank you.

826
01:24:58,557 --> 01:25:02,900
