890
01:30:57,948 --> 01:30:59,889
[SPEAKER_02]: I think we're all much more knowledgeable because of it.

891
01:31:00,249 --> 01:31:04,250
[SPEAKER_02]: And I think we're all eager to get that list and the presentation as well.

892
01:31:04,290 --> 01:31:05,310
[SPEAKER_02]: So thank you for that.

