903
01:32:08,893 --> 01:32:25,776
[SPEAKER_00]: But I think in order to hold us accountable, it'd be great to have, and this is a note for the city, great to have some sort of reporting system, some software that we use, that we publish on our website as well, so that everyone can kind of keep track.

904
01:32:26,236 --> 01:32:36,538
[SPEAKER_00]: And maybe there's some interdepartmental system that we can use to coordinate between departments on projects as well.

905
01:32:39,196 --> 01:32:41,298
