[SPEAKER_01]: What are our total needs.

914
01:33:13,081 --> 01:33:29,594
[SPEAKER_01]: And we've had discussions about this with our finance director Dickinson before as well and we know that some of those, some of some of what goes into that total need assessment is very difficult, like when it comes to the human resource capacity needs and carrying out all the projects that we could fit into an exhaustive list.

915
01:33:32,645 --> 01:33:42,891
[SPEAKER_01]: But I think that, you know where this really comes into when we get beyond just the winnowed five year list I think that what the city really needs is the exhaustive look

916
