[SPEAKER_04]: executive Councilor Collins said how we can take the information we learned in this presentation to inform the work that we're currently doing to establish an ordinance to assess our overall needs for our operating budget and our capital budget.

934
01:34:53,469 --> 01:34:54,310
[SPEAKER_04]: And to also

935
